<Legend>
      <filterByMap type="bool">false</filterByMap>
    </Legend>

----------

In QGIS project the filterbyMap function is related with "Filter Legend By Map Content" tool. 

Sugestion: This action should not be activated when we have "layouts by themes". In other words, the themes that are based on specified info from layers - categorized (symbol) - the filter map legend tool should not be actived. 

